node.text:
We’ve made purchase agreements for 2️⃣7️⃣0️⃣ new aircraft – the largest order in our history and biggest by a single airline in a decade.⁣⁣
 ⁣⁣
Meet our signature interior, your new onboard experience which will be on board our new planes from @boeing and @airbus as well as retrofitted on all other narrow-body planes planned by 2025. ⁣⁣
 ⁣⁣
🧳 Larger overhead bins to fit one carry-on for every passenger⁣⁣
📺 Seatback entertainment and power outlets at every seat⁣⁣
🎧 Bluetooth connectivity throughout the cabin meaning your headphones connect directly to entertainment ⁣⁣
💻 Industry’s fastest available inflight WiFi⁣⁣
💺 More Economy Plus and United First seats than before ⁣⁣
 ⁣⁣
Tap the link in our bio to learn more. 🎉
